post.desc:
Just imagine what Aya used to be like before she found her calling.

And I have no goddamn clue how "風遊神事", the illustrator's [**doujin**](https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/68322907), is supposed to be pronounced. Google Translate insists it's "Fuyū Shinji", which would be the On readings – but for all I know, any of those four characters can possibly use its Kun reading.
